{"tid":1679269,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外國記者會發聲明譴責警方拘捕Hong Kong Free Press攝影記者","createTime":"2019-10-28T06:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:04:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0df11d2f1dc6b26fed53e959007568c2ec60ac5b","tid":1679269,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"網媒《Hong Kong Free Press》一名自由攝影記者May James昨日在旺角採訪期間被捕，外國記者會發表聲明，譴責警方的拘捕行動，要求就警方暴力對待記者及干擾傳媒採訪，作透明及獨立的調查。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，May James為《Hong Kong Free Press》、法新社及其他新聞機構拍攝示威相片，亦曾在外國記者會刊物分享採訪示威的經驗，昨晚被捕時有記者背心及頭盔等，被捕後被通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又提到，雖然當局說記者工作可被豁免於《禁止蒙面規例》，但數名記者昨晚採訪時，被警方要求除去用於阻隔催淚氣體或胡椒噴劑的面罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488609-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488609-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD57yGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=6a188ac8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488609-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7580f385\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488609-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"665926c5fc27b53b64a5a5d4bc5d068b454e6ad7","tid":1679269,"uid":315584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/F0WZXhW.gif\" />"},{"pid":"b0db1e73cfd38b357381562098e90649ea64aa98","tid":1679269,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"40d7a8750b6c963ad0a90e435cb7ec0de9eed563","tid":1679269,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10